        <Source><![CDATA[For Each Order EmpCod, NfeFilCod, NfePedCod, NfeEntSai, (NfeCod)
	Where EmpCod = &EmpCod
	Where NfeFilCod = &FilCod
	Where NfePedCod = &PedCod
    Where NfeEntSai = Status_EntradaSaida.Entrada
